text: Aleksandr Yuryevich Ektov (; born 30 January 1996) is a Russian football player who plays for FC Orenburg. ==Club career== He made his debut in the Russian Professional Football League for FSK Dolgoprudny on 20 July 2016 in a game against FC Solyaris Moscow. He made his Russian Football National League debut for FC Shinnik Yaroslavl on 7 July 2019 in a game against FC SKA- Khabarovsk. ==References== ==External links== * Profile by Russian Professional Football League Category:1996 births Category:People from Volokolamsky District Category:Living people Category:Russian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:PFC CSKA Moscow players Category:FC Shinnik Yaroslavl players Category:FC Orenburg players
